message.content:
I need to calculate the Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio from the given cash flow statement.

This ratio is calculated as: Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio = |Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities| / |Net Profit|

From the cash flow statement:
- Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities = -1,919,526.63
- Net Profit = 99,532.29

Taking the absolute values and calculating the ratio:
|Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities| / |Net Profit| = |-1,919,526.63| / |99,532.29| = 1,919,526.63 / 99,532.29 = 19.29

Rounding to 2 decimal places: 19.29

```json
{"solution": {'Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio': '19.29'}}
```
